        <p>If the image  is included in a MadCap Flare project, you can select one of the project's style mediums<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet1"> from the <span class="Emphasis">Medium</span> drop-down. This drop-down includes any custom mediums that you have created</MadCap:conditionalText>. The format settings you select in the other fields on this tab are then used in Flare outputs associated with that medium. The formatting options for each medium are deactivated by default. Select <span class="Emphasis">Enable Format</span>  to make selections, including Format, Color Depth, Gray Scale, and Print DPI options.</p>
